title: ALLNET IP Sensoric: Electric Tension Sensors
agents: allnet_ip_sensoric
catalog: hw/environment/allnet
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 Checks Electric Tension Sensors in ALLNET IP Sensoric devices.

 The service goes {CRIT} if the reported sensor ID is 0 and {OK} otherwise.

item:
 If a name is reported for the sensor by the device: The name and the
 sensor ID. Otherwise the sensor ID only.

discovery:
 One service is created for every electric tension sensor (function = 12).
